stimulus:
Experiment

During the task, you will view a stream of word(s), and each will be displayed for 4 seconds. Please picture the food depicted by the word in your mind on a white plate. Then you will view an image of that food item.

Please rate how much the image on the screen matches the food you depicted in your mind. You will rate each image on a scale from 0 to 10, with 0 being ‘does not match all’ and 10 being ‘perfect match’.

There are no right answers. Please rate only based on your depiction of the food in your mind.

Press "j" or "k" to continue.
You successfully completed the quiz! Press any key to begin the task.

Congratulations! This is the end of the experiment. Thank you for participating!

Your survey completion code is k6wn5bsm. Please copy and paste this code to your Amazon Mechanical Turk HIT to receive credit for your participation.

Be sure to copy the code above before you click "Finish" below.

You have to Click "Finish" to complete the experiment and submit your work.

Click "Finish" to leave the experiment.

Please rate how much the image on the screen matches the food you depicted in your mind. You will rate each image on a scale from 0 to 10, with 0 being ‘does not match all’ and 10 being ‘perfect match’.

There are no right answers. Please rate only based on your depiction of the food in your mind.

Press "j" or "k" to continue.
You successfully completed the quiz! Press any key to begin the task.

Congratulations! This is the end of the experiment. Thank you for participating!

Your survey completion code is k6wn5bsm. Please copy and paste this code to your Amazon Mechanical Turk HIT to receive credit for your participation.

Be sure to copy the code above before you click "Finish" below.

You have to Click "Finish" to complete the experiment and submit your work.

Click "Finish" to leave the experiment.
